---
// index.astro - Profile/About page (Homepage)
// Bio content only - profile sidebar is in BaseLayout

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="ChiWei Hu (William) | Portfolio">
  <section class="bio-content">
    <h2 class="bio__heading">About</h2>

    <p>
      I'm a Master's student in Computer Science at the
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://www.usc.edu/">University of Southern California (USC)</a>,
      with a background in biochemistry and systems engineering.
    </p>

    <p>
      Previously, I worked as a Software Engineer Intern at
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://about.meta.com/">Meta</a> and as a Software Engineer at
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://www.strongs.com.tw/">Strong Electro-Mechanical</a>,
      gaining experience across both large-scale tech and industrial systems.
      I received my Master's degree in Biochemistry from
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://www.ntu.edu.tw/">National Taiwan University</a> and my Bachelor's degree in Life Science from
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://www.ncku.edu.tw/">National Cheng Kung University</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="bio__heading">Experience</h2>

    <p>
      I have over two years of experience in software engineering, with a focus on backend systems, system integration, and performance-critical applications. My technical work spans C++, C#, Python, and Rust, along with experience in databases and distributed systems.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Meta, I built a Rust-based CLI debugging tool on top of Apache Thrift to crawl and analyze records from a key-value store, improving issue triaging efficiency. I also implemented webhook replay functionality in the WhatsApp Business platform to ensure reliable cross-system message delivery.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Strong, I developed automation systems for semiconductor manufacturing equipment, improving process efficiency and system reliability through SECS-based communication and real-time monitoring systems.
    </p>

    <p>
      Beyond industry experience, I have built low-level systems such as an operating system kernel and developed multimedia processing pipelines, demonstrating strong fundamentals in systems programming and performance optimization.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
